1. install Homebrew // take refrence from brew official website.
2. brew install wine-crossover.
3. download LTspice64.msi for windows from Ltspice official website and move it to Downloads folder.
4. open wine crossover from app-drawer there will b icon like üç∑.
5. change directory and install software using 
cd Downloads/
msiexec /i LTspice64.msi
6. now open new terminal window and change directry using 
cd ~/.wine/drive_c/users/crossover/Desktop
7. run the application 
./LTspice.desktop 
